text: @Chewy @FedEx  our delivery showed up like this today.  Not cool https://t.co/OdpQA6JIkM

@suburbanjim Jim, This is Teresa and I am very sorry to see that your package was damaged! I would like to send a complaint in regarding this if you would DM your name, delivery address, tracking/phone numbers and an e-mail address. Thank you

@FedExHelp If I send a complaint what exactly is that going to accomplish?  Do I get a refund?  A gift card?  An apology from the savages that destroyed my delivery box?  Or is it just a waste of my time?
@suburbanjim Hi Jim, this is Carole, Teresa stepped out. I would like to escalate this.  Please DM the requested information and I can assist you.
@FedExHelp Assist me with what??? What are you going to do for me?
